dia mengalami pendarahan internal.

00:11:09.520 --> 00:11:11.600
Karena itu, dia
mengalami keguguran.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:21.760
'Ya Tuhan!
Ibu mertuaku sedang hamil!'

00:11:27.400 --> 00:11:30.440
Aku... aku hamil!

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:36.240
Anak saya...

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:40.560
Ganga, apakah kamu kehilangannya?

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:44.320
Kamu ingin membunuh Ibu,
dan kamu kehilangan anakmu!

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:50.200
